data.description: Come sit on the front porch of this beautiful home in Taylor, AL! This delightful home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a very open and spacious kitchen and living room for the whole family to enjoy. Boasting with character and comfort, it's a unique gem in a sought-after neighborhood. This property sits on 0.54 acres with a 25x30 powered workshop in the backyard. This home is sold "AS-IS".
